fulltitle: September 11 Commission Investigation incl. John Judge and Ray McGovern (2004)
title: September 11 Commission Investigation incl. John Judge and Ray McGovern (2004)
_filename: _September 11 Commission Investigation incl. John Judge and Ray McGovern (2004).mp4
description:
July 22, 2004 | The co-founders of the 9/11 Citizens Watch issued a critique of the September 11 Commission’s report released today. The organization monitored the work of the commission and conducted its own parallel investigation, saying that the commission was not independent and that the commission’s investigative standards were too low. Victims' family members also spoke. After the presentations the participants answered reporters' questions.

For more related content, please visit: 
http://ourhiddenhistory.org/
https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
